  "description": "A silhouette of trees and a utility pole are set against a vibrant, colorful sunset sky. The sky displays a gradient of colors, moving from deep oranges and reds near the horizon to lighter yellows and pinks higher up. Wispy clouds stretch across the sky, adding texture to the scene. A power line bisects the image, connecting to the utility pole. The trees are dark and prominent in the foreground, creating a strong contrast with the bright sky. In the distant background, hints of a body of water and a suggestion of land or buildings are visible.",
